Step 2 — Add the Owning BU lookup column
In Power Apps, on the Columns tab → click + New column.
In the side panel, fill these fields. Click each label below and copy the value into Power Apps:
Display name:
Owning BU
Description:
The Business Unit that owns this Parent BP. Populated by Flow 1 via the BP-to-BU Mapping table (L1-A03). Drives BU scoping for Risk Manager visibility and downstream Control Procedure BU derivation.
Data type: Lookup
